name: 1280px-Australian Census 2011 demographic map - New South Wales by POA - BCP field 7261 Persons Public administration and safety Age 65 74 years.svg

desc.text:
Attribution: Toby Hudson based on data from the Australian Bureau of Statistics

65-74 year olds employed in the public administration and safety industry as a fraction of total employed persons aged 15 and over, in New South Wales, Australia, according to the 2011 census results. The map is divided into geographical subdivisions by Postal Area. Note the split scale above and below the median value.
